                     emmo:EMMO_967080e5_2f42_4eb2_a3a9_c58143e835f9 "External pressure applied to the test object, in Pascal."@en .


###  https://w3id.org/battery-data-alliance/ontology/battery-data-format#charging_capacity_ah
